{"id":8724,"date":"2018-01-10T23:36:09","date_gmt":"2018-01-10T16:36:09","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=8724"},"modified":"2020-02-18T11:27:40","modified_gmt":"2020-02-18T04:27:40","slug":"favicon-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/design\/favicon-la-gi","title":{"rendered":"Favicon l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao website c\u1ea7n favicon?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><strong>Favicon l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong> T\u1ea1i sao b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon cho website c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? T\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o favicon \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The difference between ordinary and extraordinary is that little extra<b>.<\/b><\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c theme wordpress hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3&nbsp; m\u1ee5c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y Favicon b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Logo. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 Favicon v\u00e0 l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Favicon l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Favicon l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean m\u1ed7i tab tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 website. Favicon hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb ngay b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh t\u00ean c\u1ee7a trang web nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t logo thu nh\u1ecf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>T\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Logo l\u00e0m Favicon?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Favicon l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat g\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a Logo nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ri\u00eang. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng Logo th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf g\u1ed3m ch\u1eef d\u1ea1ng Tagline hay Title c\u1ee7a website. Favicon l\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf ch\u1eef \u0111i b\u1edfi v\u00ec k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y xem h\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 Favicon.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/No_Favicon.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/No_Favicon-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Favicon l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" class=\"wp-image-8727\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/No_Favicon-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/No_Favicon-218x123.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/No_Favicon-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/No_Favicon-700x394.jpg 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/No_Favicon-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/No_Favicon.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>T\u1ea1i sao website c\u1ea7n Favicon<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n Favicon l\u00e0m g\u00ec khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Logo hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean m\u1ed7i trang web?&nbsp; N\u00f3 c\u00f3 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n Logo hay kh\u00f4ng? Logo \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u1eadt ra b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 Favicon tr\u00ean website c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00ec l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh y\u1ebfu sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 tab c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n khi \u0111ang m\u1edf tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong ph\u1ea7n bookmark tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng website kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u00fd do th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb8P.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>R\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng website thi\u1ebfu Favicon s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c h\u00fat h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi website c\u00f3 Favicon.&nbsp; B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n l\u01b0u m\u1ed9t trang web v\u00e0o bookmark v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t t\u1edd gi\u1ea5y tr\u1eafng hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean tab nh\u01b0 v\u1eady?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-Bookmark-1.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-Bookmark-1-1024x576.png\" alt=\"Favicon bookmark\" class=\"wp-image-8786\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-Bookmark-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-Bookmark-1-218x123.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-Bookmark-1-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-Bookmark-1-700x394.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-Bookmark-1-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-Bookmark-1.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. B\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon nh\u01b0 v\u1eady ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u1ed7 l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ti\u00eau gi\u1ea3n h\u1ebft ch\u1eef tr\u00ean Logo. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"\/design\/tu-thiet-ke-logo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"\u201cT\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo trong 5 ph\u00fat\u201d (opens in a new tab)\">\u201cT\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo trong 5 ph\u00fat\u201d<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi <a href=\"\/out\/canva\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Canva (opens in a new tab)\">Canva<\/a> ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Xin nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c l\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf ch\u1eef ra kh\u1ecfi Logo l\u00e0 nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u01b0a logo v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo xong, b\u1ea1n l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 copy ra th\u00eam m\u1ed9t project m\u1edbi. B\u1ecf ph\u1ea7n ch\u1eef \u0111i th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ngay Favicon. Logo v\u00e0 Favicon s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nh\u00ecn c\u00f3 v\u1ebb chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/So-s\u00e1nh-Faicon-v\u00e0-Logo.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"385\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/So-s\u00e1nh-Faicon-v\u00e0-Logo-1024x385.png\" alt=\"So s\u00e1nh Favicon v\u00e0 Logo\" class=\"wp-image-8784\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/So-s\u00e1nh-Faicon-v\u00e0-Logo-1024x385.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/So-s\u00e1nh-Faicon-v\u00e0-Logo-218x82.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/So-s\u00e1nh-Faicon-v\u00e0-Logo-300x113.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/So-s\u00e1nh-Faicon-v\u00e0-Logo-700x263.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/So-s\u00e1nh-Faicon-v\u00e0-Logo-768x289.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/So-s\u00e1nh-Faicon-v\u00e0-Logo.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u1ee3i \u00fd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon chu\u1ea9n h\u01a1n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>\u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Favicon n\u00ean l\u00e0 PNG. \u0110\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9n \u1ea3nh.<\/li><li>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc file ph\u1ea3i &lt;100 KB.<\/li><li>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc Favicon ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n hi\u1ec7n nay n\u00ean l\u00e0 512&#215;512 px. B\u1edfi v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Retina c\u1ee7a Apple hay m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh 4K c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t Favicon c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb s\u1eafc n\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Favicon l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c r\u00fat g\u1ecdn Logo. Ngay k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi Logo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Favicon d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc. \u0110\u00f4i khi m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y \u1edf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon v\u00e0 Logo song h\u00e0nh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Logo sang Favicon theo kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>LOGO &#8211; TEXT = FAVICON<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Favicon nh\u01b0 \u00fd v\u00e0 h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0o nh\u00e9.\n<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Favicon l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Favicon cho website c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? T\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o favicon \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":9185,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[43],"tags":[18],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-l\u00e0-g\u00ec-T\u1ea1i-sao-website-c\u1ea7n-favicon.jpg",1200,600,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-l\u00e0-g\u00ec-T\u1ea1i-sao-website-c\u1ea7n-favicon-300x150.jpg",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-l\u00e0-g\u00ec-T\u1ea1i-sao-website-c\u1ea7n-favicon-700x350.jpg",700,350,true],"medium_large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Favicon-l\u00e0-g\u00ec-T\u1ea1i-sao-website-c\u1